If $A_1=\emptyset$ this is immediate. Thus suppose $A_1\ne\emptyset$, consequently ${^\star} A_1\ne\emptyset$.{\par\medskip}

Firstly, denote $g(x_2,\ldots,x_n):=(\exists x_1\in A_1)f(x_1,\ldots,x_n)$.
